# =============================================================================
# Trivy Security Scanner - Ignore File (2025 Configuration)
# =============================================================================
# This file excludes known false positives and non-critical findings
# for the Nephoran Intent Operator Kubernetes project
# Only add items here after careful security review
# =============================================================================

# Format:
# - CVE-YYYY-NNNNN: Ignore specific CVE
# - GHSA-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx: Ignore GitHub Security Advisory
# - path/to/file: Ignore vulnerabilities in specific file
# - exp:YYYY-MM-DD: Set expiration date for ignore rule

# =============================================================================
# Go Vulnerabilities - False Positives or Accepted Risks
# =============================================================================

# Example: Old etcd client library - not used in production paths
# CVE-2023-39325 exp:2025-06-01
# CVE-2023-44487 exp:2025-06-01

# Common False Positives for Kubernetes Operators
**/go.sum
**/go.mod

# =============================================================================
# Container/OS Vulnerabilities - Base Image Issues
# =============================================================================

# Distroless base image - these are often false positives
# due to stripped binaries and minimal attack surface

# Container and Deployment Configs (scanned separately)
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/k8s/**
**/kubernetes/**
**/manifests/**

# =============================================================================
# Development and Build Artifacts - Not in Production Container
# =============================================================================

# VCS and CI/CD
**/.git/**
**/.github/**

# Node.js artifacts
**/node_modules/**
**/yarn.lock
**/package-lock.json
**/package.json

# Build artifacts
**/vendor/**
**/bin/**
**/dist/**
**/.cache/**
**/tmp/**

# Build System Files
**/Makefile*
**/CMakeLists.txt
**/build.gradle*
**/pom.xml

# Build tools and linters
.golangci.yml
hack/
scripts/

# IDE and Editor Files
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~

# =============================================================================
# Test Dependencies and Data - Not in Production
# =============================================================================

# Vulnerabilities in test-only dependencies
# These don't affect production deployments
test/
testdata/
*_test.go
**/test/**
**/tests/**
**/example/**
**/examples/**
**/sample/**
**/samples/**
**/fixtures/**
vendor/github.com/stretchr/testify

# =============================================================================
# Documentation - No executable code
# =============================================================================

**/*.md
**/*.txt
**/*.rst
**/*.adoc
**/*.pdf
docs/
**/LICENSE*
**/NOTICE*
**/CHANGELOG*
**/README*

